{"tid":2176250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂華娛樂被北京以「有損國格」行政處罰！　爆全因EVERGLOW參加南韓軍隊慰勞表演","createTime":"2020-08-27T03:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T12:12:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1e74ff2c23415a0cd86b3d137d2acb505ffeb5f7","tid":2176250,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:35:41.000Z","msg":"經紀公司樂華娛樂除了北京的總部，在南韓也有開設子公司並經營偶像團體，像是宇宙少女、EVERGLOW和炯燮x義雄等人，近日他們被以北京市文化執法總隊以「有損國格」緣由判行政懲罰，傳出是因為EVERGLOW曾到南韓陸軍進行慰問表演，官方也在27日凌晨發出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5100/5100060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5100%2F5100060.jpg&h=95dc4dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲EVERGLOW曾在2019年6月28日參加南韓陸軍的慰勞表演。（圖／翻攝自Everglow Fan YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nEVERGLOW於2019年6月28日曾參加南韓國防TV的《慰勞列車》，並帶來精采歌曲《Bon Bon Chocolat》表演，近日傳出因為這場表演，樂華娛樂在今年5月18日被北京市文化執法總隊處以行政處罰，處罰依據為大陸的《文化部涉外文化藝術表演及展覽規定》中的第40條第一款第六項（從事有損國格人格演出或展覽活動）。<br />\n<br />\n相關消息爆出後，「樂華娛樂被行政處罰」跟著登上微博熱搜引起討論，樂華娛樂在27日凌晨透過官方微博發聲明，「對於樂華娛樂韓國子公司在工作對接中出現的問題，由此產生的負面影響，我們深表遺憾且致以誠摯歉意，並已接受相關行政處罰」，最後他們強調「我司與祖國立場堅定一致，拒絕一切有損國家利益的行為」，但外界若對旗下藝人發表不實的毀謗，他們也會透過法律維護藝人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5100/5100062.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5100%2F5100062.jpg&h=d7f94ac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲樂華娛樂聲明。（圖／翻攝自樂華娛樂微博）<br />\n<br />\n大陸網友在樂華娛樂的聲明下表示，「表演藝術是為大眾服務的，藝術表演應該有底線，離開了人民的支持，藝術的價值也就不存在了」、「國家利益面前無粉圈，請樂華認真整改，也請樂華保護好無故受牽連藝人」、「國家利益高於一切！請勿造謠無關藝人」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5100/5100061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5100%2F5100061.jpg&h=59764d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼大陸網友回應。（圖／翻攝自樂華娛樂、娛樂有飯微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5100/5100425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5100%2F5100425.jpg&h=893bb2af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E1_zGNdwYeY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE1_zGNdwYeY&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=62b28f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E1_zGNdwYeY</a><br />\n<br />\n怡人小姐姐好無辜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80aebe95e910ca386dd574c840e4ebce4edb501","tid":2176250,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:37:34.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6796de77631d6d9e0c9b0c24b75ac2d41e93fb","tid":2176250,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"bf607caaf89368fa7c5301cea65b7ace758243a3","tid":2176250,"uid":237517,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:44:56.000Z","msg":"韓國組合係韓國表演都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇韓國組合唔比係韓國講韓文"},{"pid":"d9258f69452c024eebaf2203d984fec4b0c57e9f","tid":2176250,"uid":68678,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"everglow 番支那出道把啦🤣🤣🤣🤣"},{"pid":"61771aeccb8b70a455a1c40f8e4a2f095bad7a5f","tid":2176250,"uid":68678,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"12one yena 幾時俾國家罰✊🏻💘<br />\n中國公司學人做韓國國民女團🤣🤣🤣🤙🏻"},{"pid":"864324ec2fec12ef7efa4f79340f791cbf3f2b56","tid":2176250,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"支那女團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dcb7a4848f8d871356d782d9b70f9ec6f26c22","tid":2176250,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"慰安女團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d0ce